---
title: Beyond Meat® Quick Irish-Style Stew with Garlic Crostini
description: In this hearty twist on a classic potato and Beyond Meat® stew, we've swapped in quick-cooking beyond meat so your meal will be on the table in less than 40 min. Don't forget to wipe the bowl clean with a slice of garlic crostini!
